item.title: Source problem help please
item.dc:creator: @jackabe jackabe
item.description:
@jackabe wrote:

OK, simple fix.

You need to place the cache in server/data. If there is a file named cache already there, replace it with the cache you have. If there isn’t one there just drag it in and run the server.

Problem solved.
